92
0:04:23.26,000 --> 0:04:26,000
One woman shoots her face. One woman shoots her husband.

93
0:04:26.26,000 --> 0:04:28,000
One woman straps herself.

94
0:04:28.26,000 --> 0:04:3,000
One woman gives birth to a baby.

95
0:04:30.26,000 --> 0:04:32,000
One woman gives birth to borders.

96
0:04:32.26,000 --> 0:04:35,000
One woman no longer believes love will ever find her.

97
0:04:35.26,000 --> 0:04:37,000
One woman never did.

98
0:04:37.26,000 --> 0:04:4,000
Where do refugee hearts go?

99
0:04:40.26,000 --> 0:04:42,000
Broken, dissed,

100
